                 ✔ RESOLVED: vanilla Header format @done(26-07-18) (was the one open risk — display
                    names live in asset bundles and weren't inspectable offline. Playtest log settled
                    it: raw header is "Benediction Cannon MkIII" — vanilla DOES embed the mark, with
                    NO space before the numeral. The case-insensitive regex matches "MkIII" and the
                    strip-then-append rewrite produces "Benediction Cannon Mk IV" correctly, so the
                    append-fallback path is never taken for English names. Keep the LogDebug: it's
                    the cheapest early warning if a game update changes the naming convention.)
